{"type": "article", "id": 32086, "title": "王大仁与 adidas Originals 合作，以及，Zara出秋冬职场着装指南 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-12T02:18:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12570, "name": "拍立得"}, {"id": 32653, "name": "军事迷彩"}, {"id": 32654, "name": "一周穿搭"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 2041, "name": "Jimmy Choo"}, {"id": 3120, "name": "Levi's"}, {"id": 8874, "name": "Fujifilm"}, {"id": 17793, "name": "洲际酒店集团"}, {"id": 23130, "name": "ENGINEERED GARMENTS"}, {"id": 21033, "name": "Tamara Mellon"}, {"id": 32655, "name": "铃木大器"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160912085837cfSZY31e9z4MUQFR.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/timo-weiland-style-director-crowne-plaza-brand-americas-uniforms-10534306/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>洲际酒店集团任命 Timo Weiland 为旗下的皇冠假日酒店美国区的造型顾问</b></a> | 作为皇冠假日酒店加速发展计划的一部分，时尚设计师 Timo Weiland 将为美国区的皇冠假日酒店设计新的制服，新的制服将在延续酒店的经典风格基础上变得更加时尚。据称，整个酒店的加速发展项目计划斥资 2 亿美元。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/jimmy-choo-said-tamara-mellon-claim-groundless-accessories-footwear-shoes-employment-noncompete-legal-10534277/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Jimmy Choo 否认了来自 Tamara Mellon 的指控</b></a> | Tamara Mellon 是 Jimmy Choo 的联合创始人，她于 2011 年离开 Jimmy Choo，并且于 2013 年开创个人品牌。Mellon 指控 Jimmy Choo 对其品牌的供应商的施压，给 Mellon 品牌带来了负面影响，并要求 400 万美元以上的赔偿。上周，Jimmy Choo 的发言人在曼哈顿高级法庭上称，该指控是没有根据的。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/ohare-named-global-vp-brand-communications-at-adidas-originals-core-10534110/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Alegra O’Hare 被任命为 Adidas Originals 的全球副总裁，负责品牌的营销传播</b></a> | 这是 Adidas Originals 的一个新的职位，Alegra O’Hare 将负责为 Adidas Originals, Adidas Neo, Y-3 多个品牌制定营销策略，以及为 Adidas 的核心球鞋团队寻求时尚合作。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/trends-analysis/revolve-asos-topshop-earned-media-value-10526459/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Revolve、Asos 和 Topshop 是 2016 年第二季度最具媒体价值的三个时尚品牌</b></a> | 社交媒体分析机构 Tribe Dynamics 评出了 2016 年第二季度最具媒体价值的三个时尚品牌。该项指标中包括品牌的社交媒体参与度、宣传渠道的影响力以及品牌自身在数字媒体中的成长性。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/retail-features/whistles-expands-middle-east-al-tayer-group-10532748/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国服饰品牌 Whistles 进军中东市场</b></a> | Whistles 是一个因为凯特王妃的青睐而大热的英国服饰品牌，它独家授权中东最大的奢侈品零售商 Al Tayer 集团，在迪拜 City Walk 开设了第一家半户外式的门店，作为进军中东市场的开端。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：&nbsp;</h3><p>设计师铃木大器所主理的时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/engineered-garments-2016-fall-winter-first-drop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Engineered Garments 发布 2016 秋冬系列新作</a>。以靛蓝、深灰以及军绿色来演绎 Engineered Garments 一贯的成熟简约风格。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090110loHGEpSzvfLJ8Ouh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090110tNXzRKViT87yE5j2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120901106xlbmdMR3EY9Fqfh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090110rvHsofAlZMzOyC5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120901193Pc9fTgs5DhLZGmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090131hXYTlkHJGAg1Laqi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/levis-camo-fw-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Levi’s 秋冬迷彩系列</a>登场，以军事迷彩风格重新定义品牌的牛仔时尚。该系列现已于 Levi’s 各大门店开售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090145KFDtGAyiYSBWqwPm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090146Lq43FWMNUCBTrspz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090146flAO94emQMBpo7UN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090146ZNDawXIvyb9ku63i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090146Wp4ruUTeVqc1ZvmP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090157iu0heqICkAOoXEdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090158ISlwt5dNPOjFqKEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120902109zl2ZxO7WXcAdGNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090210M3jDydJl0Q7oe6EV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/adidas-originals-by-alexander-wang-first-limited-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang 与 adidas Originals 首度携手，推出联名系列</a>。该系列以标志性的黑色调展现 Alexander Wang 颠覆规则的街头时尚，同时融入了 Alexander Wang 对  adidas Originals 的三叶草 logo 的颠覆性设计，使其更具有未来感。该系列涵盖了运动外套、大衣、连帽衫等单品，售价从 80 到 200 美元不等。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090230Sdilx8I9kXUYrnhO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090230LpRWBdqPurKlGFhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090230aOGh87lUuFtT15Z3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090237f7NngJp5BRPAjwH9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090237iIfzM0KyoeCvuJNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016091209024467eYEkuTRVBQzt9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>用拍立得也可以拍出黑白照片了，Fujifilm 推出全新的黑白相纸<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/art-and-culture/fujifilm-instax-mini-monochrome-film/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> instax mini film Monochrome</a>。将于 10 月在全球进行发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120902569GiwSBoqCUOVYmgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090256nzkKTZRyu0JPGOhB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/adidas-originals-nmdc1-trail\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 发布全新鞋款 NMD_C1 Trail</a> 。这款鞋的中筒鞋身以弹力尼龙材料打造，于鞋带与后跟处拼接麂皮与皮革，整体的质感更为丰富。这系列鞋款共有灰、黑两色，将于 10 月 1 日登陆全球各大 adidas 指定店铺。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120903113VaAIDdN65bOymYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120903194VZauxWegcjsv3d2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666886\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>每天上班不知道穿什么的话，来看看 ZARA 最新的 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/lookbook/zara-monday-to-friday-fall-winter-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">「Monday to Friday」秋冬系列</a>。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090330nukPgdwGtfVZoFNJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090339KVFtnU6TgyeZLadw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090339a3JuGmo1UQtBl4eN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090339CgGjSc2BVptEeF7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090340G6jK7xkTFitCvV3y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090340g4lExA7FpHXV6PeN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090346PLduJg2eTnwImZo8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912090346HcadTYRVne71Uq8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}